  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nCurrently every database has own metric properties in Nethermind.Db.Metrics. \r\nFor example Bloom -> BloomDbReads and Blocks -> BlocksDbReads\r\nThe code that initiates these databases is not very flexible and updaters to these metrics are hardcoded and passed via delegates.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nWe could use dynamic metrics stored in the MetricsDict dictionary.\r\n\r\nRelies on #3204 \r\n",
